{
  "stem": "25938.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I read that for the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were gathered there, a few of the prisoners who came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was known that is a group [INAUDIBLE] will be there inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They came like a meeting that we brought there, and we were all reciting, the people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we came back and we analyzed that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not specifically Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My poem was not at all about Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just the dawn comes, and some-- a new dawn comes, and we are ready for--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A different type.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother and I were two different-- diametrically different types.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why I survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he was the one to manage in Auschwitz, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't able to manage, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to know all kind of tricks to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like, to change-- you had a portion to change for-- the bread for soup or the soup for cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were cigarettes there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They got a trade going, was going on there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You had to have a good group to work somehow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, well, these people saved my life, a few people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Polish-- Polish men.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a murderer, but he saved my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's interesting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I even seen him beating people to death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think the way he told me that I know-- when I came there, he was already an old [? kapo, ?] an old [?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[GERMAN] ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he told me in my face-- told me, I would have killed you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I didn't think of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Imagine-- I was running from-- who did it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was the only one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure I was the only one out of the hundreds of thousands who survived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To run away from the group, that was against the rules.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A crime.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
